<title>UK: BZW sets call warrants on Novartis.</title>
<headline>BZW sets call warrants on Novartis.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-03-12</dateline>
<text>
<p>BZW Warrants Ltd has issued 750,000 American-style call warrants, on Novatis, lead manager BZW Securities Ltd said.</p>
<p>10 warrants control one share.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE    1,900.00 CHF	    ISSUE PRICE  17.50 CHF</p>
<p> MATURITY DATE   10.MAR.99		 PAYDATE	03.APR.97</p>
<p> LISTING	   SWISS SE		  MIN EXER LOT ONE</p>
<p> SPOT REFERENCE  1,795.00 CHF</p>
<p>--Reuter London Newsroom +44 171 542 7658</p>
</text>
